nt/uploads/2025/02/linkin-park@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/linkin-park@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/linkin-park@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/linkin-park@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/linkin-park@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a> have kicked off their run of 2025 live shows, celebrating the release of <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/linkin-park-from-zero-review-3811752">&#39;From Zero&#39;</a> . Check out the tracklist and footage from the first gig below.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mike-shinoda-tells-us-about-his-love-of-sleep-token-and-supporting-emerging-talent-3548164">Mike Shinoda tells us about his love of Sleep Token and supporting emerging talent</a></strong></li></ul><p> The opening night of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-2025-world-stadium-tour-wembley-buy-tickets-3812660">2025 world tour</a> was held last weekend, as <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-shinoda">Mike Shinoda</a> and co. took to the stage at the Estadio GNP Seguros in Mexico City.</p><p> It follows on from a number of shows last year, celebrating the band&#39;s latest album – which is their first since the tragic passing of frontman <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chester-bennington">Chester Bennington</a> and sees former Dead Sara singer <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">Emily Armstrong take on vocal duties</a> .</p><p> At the gig in Mexico, the show was split into five separate acts, including the encore, and the setlist saw the members showcase tracks from across their discography – ranging from early fan favourites to some of their newest singles.</p><p> They began with the &#39;Meteora&#39; track &#39;Somewhere I Belong&#39;, before going into &#39;Hybrid Theory&#39;s &#39;Crawling&#39;, &#39;New Divide&#39; – which was written for the <em>Transformers: Revenge Of The Fallen</em> soundtrack – and the new album&#39;s lead single, &#39;The Emptiness Machine&#39;. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Bleed It Out w/ Cut The Bridge snippet [Live 4K] (Mexico City, MX - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O6LR72Cqksk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: The Emptiness Machine [Live 4K] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/clfJULqvSHA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Faint [Live 4K] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hZiXeLcBm1M?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Act II included new songs &#39;Over Each Other&#39;, &#39;Casualty&#39; and &#39;Two Faced&#39;, as well as earlier tracks like &#39;The Catalyst&#39;, &#39;Castle Of Glass&#39;, &#39;Empty Spaces&#39; and &#39;One Step Closer&#39;. Act III, on the other hand, contained notable inclusions of &#39;From Zero&#39; track &#39;All Good Things Go&#39;, and &#39;Lost&#39;, the &#39;Meteora&#39;-era track that remained unreleased until the 2023 reissue. Both were played live for the first time during the show.</p><p> Act IV saw another live debut, this time coming in the form of the &#39;From Zero&#39; track &#39;Overflow&#39;, as well as two of the band&#39;s biggest hits: &#39;Numb&#39; and &#39;In The End&#39;. The encore saw the band wrap up with back-to-back renditions of &#39;Papercut&#39;, &#39;A Place For My Head&#39;, &#39;Heavy Is The Crown&#39; and &#39;Bleed It Out&#39;.</p><p> Find more footage of the show below, as well as the complete setlist. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Good Things Go [Live Debut 4K] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HEY4SSjIKjs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Lost [Live Debut 4K - Full Band Version] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eGvQE9Y-CHs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Overflow [Live Debut 4K] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/n4YXgolsoqw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park: Casualty [Live 4K] (Mexico City, Mexico - January 31, 2025)" width="696" height="392" src="https: